  "body": "### Description\n\nI would like to mount external configuration sources which appear as a folder structure\r\n```\r\nfoo/\r\n|__num.max\r\n|__num.size\r\n```\r\n\r\nI could write my own `ConfigSource` to read the properties, or I could use the `FileSystemConfigSource` from [smallrye-config-source-file-system](https://smallrye.io/docs/smallrye-config/config-sources/config-sources.html#filesystem-config-source).\r\nUnfortunately, `smallrye-config-source-file-system` doesn't come with the Quarkus-BOM, so I have to set the version by myself.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nAdd `smallrye-config-source-file-system` to Quarkus-BOM or bring it with quarkus-core to add support for filesystem based configuration.",
